325
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:53,760
Pozivam i sve gledatelje da to proučite.

326
00:42:53,920 --> 00:42:54,800
Tako je, tako je jako.

327
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:57,760
Jeste gledali Black Mirror?

